Attention Contributors:

	If you want to contribute to Glean, please keep copyright
	issues in mind.  If you provide a bug-fix or other
	modification to an existing component, you must agree to the
	copyright on that component before submitting the change.

	If you wish to provide a new component, such as a new test,
	then it will automatically be treated according to the
	copyright above unless you apply a different one.  Allen
	reserves the right not to release new components with
	copyrights that compromise Glean's overall goals of openness
	and availability, but of course you may release such
	components as part of your own software distributions if you
	desire, subject to the constraints in the notice above.
